# Hook: Post-Plan Checklist

Trigger: After a plan is generated or completed
Purpose: Ensure the Pre-Plan Checklist is always respected before moving to execution.

Action:
- Automatically remind the user to complete `docs/checklists/pre-plan-checklist.md`
- Do not allow progression to execution until the checklist is confirmed
- Display message: "Please complete the Pre-Plan Checklist before proceeding"